## Visual Style

(Replicate the Visual Style sections provided in the PROJECT CONTEXT, ensuring exact color usage, typography, spacing, and design tokens.)

Color Palette (reiterated for reference):
- Primary background: #FBFBFC
- Map/background overlay: #F3F4F6
- Primary text: #111827
- Secondary text / meta: #6B7280
- Borders / dividers: #E5E7EB
- Card background / surfaces: #FFFFFF
- Accent (callouts / badges): #FF6B4A
- Accent (interactive / primary CTA): #0F172A
- Accent (focus / subtle highlights): #93C5FD
- Muted success/credibility accent: #10B981

Typography & Layout:
- Font family: Inter / SF Pro / system-ui
- H1: 48–56px, 700
- H2: 24–32px, 600–700
- Body: 16px, 400, line-height 1.4–1.6
- Micro: 12–14px, 500/400
- Numeric stats: 28–36px, 700
- Spacing: 12-column grid, 48–64px vertical rhythm between major sections, card padding 20–28px, controls padding 12–16px

Key Design Elements
- Card: white surface, 1px border #E5E7EB, radius 10–12px, soft shadow
- Hover states: lift and subtle shadow enhancement
- Navigation: top bar with brand on left, links, and auth actions
- Data Visualization: minimal line charts with neutral colors
- Interactive Elements: pill CTAs, inputs with 1px borders, focus blue glow

Design Philosophy
- Modern, trust-focused minimalism
- Corporate aesthetic with restrained accents
- Spatial calm and hierarchy
- Transparent UI cues for provenance and auditability
- Fast scannability and drill-down readiness

Connected Pages
- Signup Page
- Login Page

